      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes are beginning to soften, add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>curry powder</strong>,<strong> ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>black mustard seeds</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>coconut stock</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
