    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>hake fillet[s]</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped hake</strong> and <strong>halved green beans </strong>to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 5 min further or until the fish is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
