    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the hake is cooked and the green beans are tender, add the <strong>cooked rice</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the pan</p><p>Gently stir everything together – this is your <strong>one pan Keralan-style hake curry</strong></p>",
